<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>116</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu kross ei naihsak in,
 Tuikhuk lul umna chu;
 Namtin di'n damtui manbei,
 Kalvari a luong chuh.

[V2]
 Kross achun, Kross achun,
 Ka lopina um hen;
 Ka thagau kipak taka,
 Luigala a chawlh ma'n.

[V3]
 2. Thagau lau kross kienga um,
 Hehpih na'n eimu tai;
 Ziechun Zingsawl vaktak chun,
 Ka kimvel a salhvak.

[V4]
 3. Pathien Cha Kross kienga um,
 Kross umdan ei hilh in;
 Nicheng in ei panpih in,
 Kross li'm in eilieh hen.

[V5]
 4. Kross kiengah ngakzing ingka,
 Kinem taksang zingin;
 Gamnuom chu ka tun macheng,
 Luigal lehlam achun.</lyrics>
<title>NEAR THE CROSS</title>
</song>